# RZGB Project ‚Äî Cursor Rules
# Full context is in .ai-context.md ‚Äî read it first before making any changes.

## Two Brands, One Codebase
- **Zaproc** (zaproc.co.uk) ‚Äî SaaS procurement platform for manufacturing
- **RZ Global Solutions** (rzglobalsolutions.co.uk) ‚Äî bespoke component supply broker
- Domain detected at runtime in `src/lib/portalConfig.js` via `window.location.hostname`

## Stack
- React 18 + Vite (JSX only ‚Äî no TypeScript)
- Tailwind CSS (no CSS modules, no inline styles)
- Radix UI + shadcn components in `src/components/ui/`
- Lucide React for icons
- Framer Motion for animations
- Supabase for auth + database (RLS enabled, workspace_id scoped)
- React Router v6

## Import Alias
- `@/` = `src/` ‚Äî always use this, never relative `../../`

## Key Files
- `src/lib/portalConfig.js` ‚Äî domain routing logic (isRZGBDomain, isLandingDomain, getPortalUrl)
- `src/App.jsx` ‚Äî all routes and providers
- `src/contexts/AuthContext.jsx` ‚Äî useAuth() hook
- `src/pages/HomeOrRedirect.jsx` ‚Äî picks landing page by domain
- `src/pages/RZGBLandingPage.jsx` ‚Äî rzglobalsolutions.co.uk landing
- `src/pages/LandingPage.jsx` ‚Äî zaproc.co.uk landing
- `src/components/DomainGuard.jsx` ‚Äî redirects non-root paths on landing domains
- `public/.htaccess` ‚Äî SPA routing on Hostinger Apache (do not delete)

## Auth Roles
super_admin > customer_admin > client > supplier
All DB queries must be scoped by workspace_id.

## Styling
- Light theme default, dark via ThemeContext toggle
- RZGB: slate + orange-500 accent, glassmorphism (backdrop-blur, bg-white/10, border-white/20)
- Zaproc: sky blue + slate, clean minimal
- Fonts: Inter (headings) + DM Sans (body) ‚Äî loaded in index.html

## Git / Deploy
- `main` is protected ‚Äî PRs only, Build + Lint checks must pass
- Hostinger auto-deploys both sites from `main`
- `.env` is gitignored ‚Äî set VITE_SUPABASE_URL + VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY in Hostinger dashboard

## Do Not
- No TypeScript, no CSS files, no styled-components
- No react-icons (use lucide-react)
- No window.location.href for internal nav (use React Router)
- No new Supabase clients (use src/lib/supabase.js or supabaseAdmin.js)
- No console.log in production code
- Never commit .env or service role keys

## Critical Auth Safety Rules (DO NOT VIOLATE)
- `fetchProfileByUserId` in `authService.js` selects EXACTLY these 7 columns: `role, company_name, logo_url, is_demo, status, workspace_id, admin_scope` ‚Äî **NEVER add columns or joins** ‚Äî adding `onboarding_status` caused silent login failure (column may not exist on all DB instances)
- `onboarding_status` and `workspaceStatus` are loaded SEPARATELY via `fetchProfileExtras` + `fetchWorkspaceStatus` in an isolated `useEffect` in `AuthContext.jsx` ‚Äî decoupled from login flow
- Supabase PostgREST embedded selects (joins) are unreliable for this schema ‚Äî always use separate queries
- `fetchUserProfile` returns `'ok'|'missing'|'error'` string ‚Äî `handleMissingProfile` only called on `'missing'`, never `'error'`

## Joinlist / Self-Signup System (Added 2026-03-15)
- New self-signup flow: Signup ‚Üí Login ‚Üí `/onboarding` (5-step wizard) ‚Üí `/pending-approval` ‚Üí super-admin approves ‚Üí workspace active
- Workspace `status`: `pending` (new signup) ‚Üí `active` (approved) | `archived` (rejected)
- Profile `onboarding_status`: `not_started` ‚Üí `completed` (wizard done) ‚Üí `approved` / `rejected`
- DB migration `supabase/migrations/20260319000000_joinlist.sql` **MUST be run in Supabase SQL Editor**
- `ProtectedRoute` gates pending admins: `workspaceStatus === 'pending'` ‚Üí redirect `/onboarding` or `/pending-approval`
- Platform admin can approve/reject from `/platform-admin/join-requests` (`PlatformJoinlistPage`)

## Joinlist Key Files
- `src/features/onboarding/OnboardingWizard.jsx` ‚Äî 5-step self-signup wizard
- `src/features/onboarding/OnboardingDetailsPanel.jsx` ‚Äî read-only admin preview of onboarding data
- `src/pages/OnboardingPage.jsx` ‚Äî route wrapper for wizard
- `src/pages/PendingApprovalPage.jsx` ‚Äî waiting screen after wizard submit
- `src/pages/platform/PlatformJoinlistPage.jsx` ‚Äî admin approve/reject UI
- `src/services/workspaceService.js` ‚Äî saveOnboardingData, completeOnboarding, fetchPendingWorkspaces, approveWorkspace, rejectWorkspace

